{"tid":2198040,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"(NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3080 創始版開箱","createTime":"2020-09-11T05:20:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-12T12:30:12.000Z","uid":32577,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7ef3e3901e5ff05acd58b88c8c514921f480c3cf","tid":2198040,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:20:17.000Z","msg":"這一代 NVIDIA 創始版（公版）顯示卡，可說是有著顛覆以往顯卡印象的新穎設計，以往視為信仰的 GEFORCE RTX 招牌改為白色燈光，並採用著 X 形狀的一體式框架，搭配均溫板複合熱導管和散熱鰭片，通過正反 8.7mm 軸向式進風、抽風配置，打造全新的顯卡散熱設計。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-1.jpg&h=97a23fe1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr; NVIDIA GeForce RTX 3080 創始版外盒。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-3.jpg&h=d587389c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr; 這代顯卡穩穩的斜躺於包裝之內。<br />\n<br />\n這代最容易讓人混淆的就是，創始版將以往的顯卡背面設計為正面，露處 X 框架的線條，高質感霧黑的背板，上頭印著 RTX 3080 的字樣，以及背面的軸向式抽風扇。<br />\n<br />\n而以往的顯卡正面，則是同樣展露 X 框架，並全面改以散熱鰭片，通過熱導管將廢熱引導至顯卡前端，提升整體的散熱效果，也可帶動機殼內部的氣流。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-4.jpg&h=df423185&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr; RTX 3080 正面美照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-6.jpg&h=9d6736f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr; RTX 3080 背面，X 框架與滿滿的散熱鰭片。<br />\n<br />\n縮小電路板、改造散熱器之後，這代 RTX 3080 創始版，尺寸來到 285 x 112 mm、2 Slot 插槽設計，換句話說比起上一代 RTX 20 創始版還要長了 2cm；此外，顯卡重量也來到 1.385kg，比起上一代重了 122g。<br />\n<br />\n此外，因為電路板縮小並改用 PCIe 12-pin 供電接頭，使得出線處位於顯卡的中段，若在家上轉接線之後，這出線位置勢必讓理線魔人心煩，也只能透過日後客製線來美化了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-7.jpg&h=51cd3666&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr; 顯卡側面，GEFORCE RTX 字樣，以及 PCIe 12-pin 供電接頭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-11.jpg&h=ad2e178b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 這代顯卡較長 28.5cm。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-12.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-12.jpg&h=23a11068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr; 高度同樣是 2 Slot 佔用。<br />\n<br />\nRTX 3080 創始版同樣提供 4 影像輸出，分別為 HDMI 2.1 與 3 個 DisplayPort 1.4a 連接埠，新的 HDMI 2.1 支援到 4K120Hz 與 8K60Hz 輸出，連接線頻寬達到 4 線共 48Gbps，並支援 Variable Refresh Rate 功能。<br />\n<br />\n但未來 G-Sync 螢幕是否開放 HDMI 2.1 支援，這點就要看 NVIDIA 的規劃了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-10.jpg&h=61841715&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr; 影像輸出埠。<br />\n<br />\n配件中包含產品的說明文件，以及相當重要的 PCIe 12-pin 轉 2 個 PCIe 8-pin 的轉接線，NVIDIA 建議使用原廠線材，除非客製端明確了解接頭配置。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-26.jpg&h=9e662257&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr; 創始版配件。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-28.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-28.jpg&h=8bec3065&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&uarr; PCIe 12-pin 轉 2 個 PCIe 8-pin 的轉接線。<br />\n<br />\n目前還無法跟各位分享 RTX 3080 的效能，但請記住創始版解禁時間為 9/14 晚上 21:00，屆時會有完整的測試報告與直播跟各位分享，而 AIC 自製卡則是 9/17 晚上 21:00 開賣與解禁，相升級的玩家請再等等。<br />\n<img src=\"https://p.xfastest.com/~sinchen/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080/NVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-27.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp.xfastest.com%2F~sinchen%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080%2FNVIDIA-GeForce-RTX-3080-27.jpg&h=52cc22c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.xfastest.com/nvidia/85220/nvidia-geforce-rtx-3080-open-box/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.xfastest.com%2Fnvidia%2F85220%2Fnvidia-geforce-rtx-3080-open-box%2F&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fgDrJ99PsHpDQ3gYSBhgLgU%3D&h=c69c5bf8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.xfastest.com/nvidia/85220/nvidia-geforce-rtx-3080-open-box/</a>"},{"pid":"2f9b2df9778460312ff124f9d6def1409347c7c8","tid":2198040,"uid":32577,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又要俾人顯你老母"},{"pid":"c13dd203e89d4b64137f921afd5ae7e4f8d20013","tid":2198040,"uid":2772,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:28:33.000Z","msg":"你老母顯靈"},{"pid":"7fd40207ccf09fb1b775f3703e2e4af94e145647","tid":2198040,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T05:29:12.000Z","msg":"轉接線....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">危</span></strong>"},{"pid":"830ab765b6a33bfcfc12ee37802ac4e66d72493f","tid":2198040,"uid":32577,"like":1,"